    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您被困在一个您认识的水池中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细观察周围环境，设法逃离水池。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个游戏是一个搜索异常点的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果没有发现任何异常现象，则继续前进；如果发现了异常现象，则返回。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194300/extras/54a32eedffa2181b9232ed9fcfd81fe0.poster.avif?t=1729586928\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194300/extras/54a32eedffa2181b9232ed9fcfd81fe0.webm?t=1729586928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194300/extras/54a32eedffa2181b9232ed9fcfd81fe0.mp4?t=1729586928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款类似于 “8 号出口 ”的游戏，灵感来自于 “8 号出口 ”游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中包含一些小惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供提示，帮助您发现异常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于提示功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成游戏后，提示功能将被激活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在泳池区域使用提示功能可以帮助您发现异常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏时间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 至 60 分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD - 移动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E - 互动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift - 运行</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESC - 设置</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空格 - 提示功能（*游戏通关后释放）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选项。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果游戏运行速度太慢，请调整设置以降低画质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于播放视频和分发</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎您现场玩游戏和发布游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如有可能，请在视频摘要中加入我们商店页面的链接，我们将不胜感激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
